    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new, you\u2019ve gotta come see this one. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
