    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in truly pristine condition. This specimen represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation, featuring flawless coachwork and an interior that remains in showroom state. Meticulously serviced and handled with the utmost care, its mechanical performance is as impeccable as its aesthetic presentation. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to secure a vehicle of unrivaled integrity and distinction. We invite you to experience a standard of quality that is increasingly difficult to source in the current market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
