      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014honestly, it still smells new! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
