      "description": "This E46 M3 is an impeccable specimen of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, breathing through six individual throttle bodies. This example features a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a reinforced rear subframe, comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and rod bearing replacement with high-performance shells. The chassis remains taut with original suspension geometry, and the bodywork retains its factory depth and luster. A true collector-grade driver's car with zero mechanical compromises.",
